        1.  PEP (post-exposure prophylaxis) is when a person is given medicine right after getting exposed
            to HIV (like after unprot
        2.  PEP (post-exposure prophylaxis) is when a person is given medicine right after getting exposed
            to HIV (like after unprotected sex with an infected partner) to prevent becoming infected.
            Before today, had you heard of PEP?

        1.  Research is also being done to develop an HIV vaccine, that is, a shot or series of shots that
            would prevent someone fro
        2.  Research is also being done to develop an HIV vaccine, that is, a shot or series of shots that
            would prevent someone from being infected if they were exposed to HIV or that would keep them
            healthy longer if they were infected with HIV. It would be like vaccines people already get to
            prevent measles or polio. Before today, have you ever heard of an HIV vaccine?

      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      selfdiag                                                      Positive Diagnosis by Self Report (SR)
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      
                        type:  numeric (double)
                       label:  selfdiag
      
                       range:  [0,1]                        units:  1
               unique values:  2                        missing .:  1/507
             unique mv codes:  2                       missing .*:  25/507
      
                  tabulation:  Freq.   Numeric  Label
                                 279         0  NO
                                 202         1  YES
                                   1         .  
                                  25        .c  NA
      
      selfdiag:
        1.  cap nois replace selfdiag=w1_selfdiag if !mi(w1_selfdiag)
        2.  cap nois replace selfdiag=.c if mi(w1_selfdiag) & mi(selfdiag) & w1_labdata!="YES":w1_labdata
            & hivnumtests<1
        3.  cap nois replace selfdiag = 1 if (hivstatus2=="HIV+":hivstatus2)
        4.  cap nois replace selfdiag=w2_selfdiag if !mi(w2_selfdiag)
        5.  cap nois replace selfdiag=.c if mi(w2_selfdiag) & mi(selfdiag) & w2_labdata!="YES":w2_labdata
            & hivnumtests<1
        6.  cap nois replace selfdiag = 1 if (hivstatus2=="HIV+":hivstatus2)
        7.  CASCADE module

        1.  CASCADE module
      
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      ltcwithin6                                           Linked to Care Within 6 Months of Diagnosis, SR
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      
                        type:  numeric (double)
                       label:  ltcwithin6
      
                       range:  [0,1]                        units:  1
               unique values:  2                        missing .:  0/507
             unique mv codes:  2                       missing .*:  315/507
      
                  tabulation:  Freq.   Numeric  Label
                                  53         0  NO
                                 139         1  YES
                                   4        .a  DON'T KNOW
                                 311        .c  NA
      
      ltcwithin6:
        1.  replace ltcwithin6 = w1_ltcwithin6 if !mi(w1_ltcwithin6)
        2.  replace ltcwithin6 = hivgomdpostpos_unit if mi(hivgomdpostpos_unit) & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
            & mi(ltcwithin6)
        3.  replace ltcwithin6 = 0 if mi(w1_ltcwithin6') & !mi(hivgomdpostpos_amt) &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
        4.  replace ltcwithin6 = 0 if mi(w1_ltcwithin6') & !mi(hivgomdpostpos_unit) &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
        5.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w1_ltcwithin6) & hivgomdpostpos_unit=="DAYS":hivgomdpostpos_unit
            & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=182 & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
        6.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w1_ltcwithin6) & hivgomdpostpos_unit=="WEEKS":hivgomdpostpos_unit
            & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=26 & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
        7.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w1_ltcwithin6) &
            hivgomdpostpos_unit=="MONTHS":hivgomdpostpos_unit & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=6 &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
        8.  replace ltcwithin6 = .c if selfdiag!="YES":selfdiag & mi(ltcwithin6)
        9.  replace ltcwithin6 = w2_ltcwithin6 if !mi(w2_ltcwithin6)
       10.  replace ltcwithin6 = hivgomdpostpos_unit if mi(hivgomdpostpos_unit) & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
            & mi(ltcwithin6)
       11.  replace ltcwithin6 = 0 if mi(w2_ltcwithin6') & !mi(hivgomdpostpos_amt) &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
       12.  replace ltcwithin6 = 0 if mi(w2_ltcwithin6') & !mi(hivgomdpostpos_unit) &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
       13.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w2_ltcwithin6) & hivgomdpostpos_unit=="DAYS":hivgomdpostpos_unit
            & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=182 & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
       14.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w2_ltcwithin6) & hivgomdpostpos_unit=="WEEKS":hivgomdpostpos_unit
            & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=26 & selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
       15.  replace ltcwithin6 = 1 if mi(w2_ltcwithin6) &
            hivgomdpostpos_unit=="MONTHS":hivgomdpostpos_unit & hivgomdpostpos_amt<=6 &
            selfdiag=="YES":selfdiag
       16.  replace ltcwithin6 = .c if selfdiag!="YES":selfdiag & mi(ltcwithin6)
       17.  CASCADE module

            labinfected=="YES":labinfected
        2.  CDPH:replace labsuppressed = labsuppressed_uconnect if mi(labsuppressed)
        3.  CDPH update:replace labsuppressed = "YES":labsuppressed if labrnabin=="NO":labrnabin &
            mi(labsuppressed) & labinfected=="YES":labinfected
        4.  CASCADE module

      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      labrnaorig                                     HIV RNA Original Result String copies/mL blood by Lab
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      
                        type:  string (str50), but longest is str49
      
               unique values:  62                       missing "":  108/507
      
                    examples:  ""
                               "Not Detected"
                               "Not Detected"
                               "Not Detected"
      
                     warning:  variable has embedded blanks
      
      labrnaorig:
        1.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        2.  CASCADE module
      
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      labrna                                                         HIV RNA Result copies/mL blood by Lab
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      
                        type:  numeric (long)
                       label:  labrna, but 56 nonmissing values are not labeled
      
                       range:  [0,521513]                   units:  1
               unique values:  56                       missing .:  0/507
             unique mv codes:  2                       missing .*:  104/507
      
                    examples:  0     
                               0     
                               0     
                               .b    NA-QNS
      
      labrna:
        1.  g labrna = regexs(3) + regexs(5) + regexs(7) + regexs(9) if regexm(lower(hiv1rnaresult),
            "([a-z]*)(<*)([0-9]+)(,*)([0-9]+)(,*)([0-9]+)(,*)([0-9]+)")
        2.  destring labrna, replace
        3.  replace labrna = .b if labrna <= 2000
        4.  replace labrna = 0 if labrna == . & !mi(labrnaorig)
        5.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        6.  replace labrna = .c if labrna==. & labdata=="NO":labdata
        7.  CDPH:replace labrna = w3labrna if (mi(labrna) & !mi(w3labrna)) &
            labinfected=="YES":labinfected
        8.  CDPH:replace labrna = labrna_uconnect if mi(labrna)
        9.  CASCADE module
      
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                        type:  numeric (long)

                       range:  [0,1]                        units:  1

      labchronic:
        1.  g labchronic = 0 if (!mi(labgen4) & !mi(labmultispot))
        2.  replace labchronic =.c if mi(labgen4) & mi(labmultispot)
        3.  replace labchronic=1 if (labgen4==1 & labmultispot==1) | (labgen4==0 & labmultispot==1 &
            labrnabin==1)
        4.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        5.  replace labchronic = .c if labchronic==. & labdata=="NO":labdata
        6.  replace labchronic = .c if mi(labmultispot)

        3.  replace labrctacute = 0 if mi(labmultispot) & labgen4==0
        4.  replace labrctacute = 1 if (labgen4==1 & labmultispot==0)
        5.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result

        7.  replace labrctacute = .c if mi(labgen4)

        4.  replace labacute = 1 if (labgen4==0 & labrnabin==1)
        5.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        6.  replace labacute = .c if mi(labrnabin)

      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      labinfected                                                             HIV Infected, by Lab Results
      ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      
                        type:  numeric (double)
                       label:  labinfected

        1.  egen labinfected= rowmax(labchronic labrctacute labacute)
        2.  replace labinfected =.c if (mi(labgen4) & mi(labmultispot)) & (mi(labgen4) & mi(labrnabin))
        3.  replace labinfected = .c if (mi(labchronic) & mi(labrctacute) & mi(labacute))
        4.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        5.  replace labinfected = .c if labinfected==. & labdata=="NO":labdata
        6.  replace labinfected = .c if (mi(labchronic) & mi(labrctacute) & mi(labacute))
        7.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace labinfected = w1_labinfected if mi(labinfected) &
            w1_labinfected=="YES":w1_labinfected
        8.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace labinfected = w2_labinfected if mi(labinfected) &
            w2_labinfected=="YES":w2_labinfected
        9.  CDPH Data:replace labinfected = "YES":labinfected if cdph_hivdiagwhen=="Before
            W1":cdph_hivdiagwhen
       10.  CDPH Data:replace labinfected = "YES":labinfected if cdph_hivdiagwhen=="Before
            W2":cdph_hivdiagwhen
       11.  CDPH Data:replace labinfected = "YES":labinfected if cdph_hivdiagwhen=="Before
            W3":cdph_hivdiagwhen

            !mi(w2idate) & !mi(cdph_hivdiagdate)

            !mi(w3idate) & !mi(cdph_hivdiagdate)
        4.  replace cdph_hivdiagwhen = 3 if cdph_hivdiagdate > w3idate & mi(cdph_hivdiagwhen) &
            !mi(w3idate) & !mi(cdph_hivdiagdate)

            cdph_ltcwithin6 cdph_hivdiagwhen cdph_hivdiagdate w1idate w2idate w3idate, by(su_id)
        4.  replace cdph_ltcwithin6 = .c if cdph_hivdiagwhen>"Before W3":cdph_hivdiagwhen
        5.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace cdph_ltcwithin6 = w1_cdph_ltcwithin6 if mi(cdph_ltcwithin6) &
            !mi(w1_cdph_ltcwithin6)
        6.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace cdph_ltcwithin6 = w2_cdph_ltcwithin6 if mi(cdph_ltcwithin6) &
            !mi(w2_cdph_ltcwithin6)

        2.  replace labinfected =.c if (mi(labgen4) & mi(labmultispot)) & (mi(labgen4) & mi(labrnabin))
        3.  replace labinfected = .c if (mi(labchronic) & mi(labrctacute) & mi(labacute))
        4.  Derived from Wave 2 Bloospot Lab Result
        5.  replace labinfected = .c if labinfected==. & labdata=="NO":labdata
        6.  replace labinfected = .c if (mi(labchronic) & mi(labrctacute) & mi(labacute))
        7.  WAVE 2 CHANGE:replace labinfected = w1_labinfected if mi(labinfected) &
            w1_labinfected=="YES":w1_labinfected
        8.  CDPH Data:replace labinfected = "YES":labinfected if cdph_hivdiagwhen=="Before
            W1":cdph_hivdiagwhen
        9.  CDPH Data:replace labinfected = "YES":labinfected if cdph_hivdiagwhen=="Before
            W2":cdph_hivdiagwhen
       10.  CASCADE module
       11.  CASCADE module

        2.  destring labrna, replace

        4.  replace labrna = 0 if labrna == . & !mi(labrnaorig)

            Wave 2 and Wave 3 with previous positive infection by Uconnect lab only. It does not include
            previous or current CDPH labs.
       10.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace labinfected_uconnect = w1_labinfected_notimputed if
            (labinfected_uconnect=="NO":labinfected_uconnect | mi(labinfected_uconnect)) &
            w1_labinfected_notimputed=="YES":w1_labinfected_notimputed
       11.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace labinfected_uconnect = w2_labinfected_notimputed if
            (labinfected_uconnect=="NO":labinfected_uconnect | mi(labinfected_uconnect)) &
            w2_labinfected_notimputed=="YES":w2_labinfected_notimputed

      cdph_earliestafterdiag                     CDPH: Earliest Date After CDPH HIV Diagnosis Date (N=146)

      cdph_earliestafterdiag:
        1.  bysort su_id : egen cdph_earliestafterdiag = min(cdph_sample_dt) if cdph_sample_dt!=
            cdph_hivdiagdate

        3.  replace cdph_earliestafterdiag = cdph_earliestafterdiag if mi(cdph_earliestafterdiag)
        4.  Collapsed from cdph_test data: collapse (max) cdph_earliestafterdiag cdph_sample_when
            cdph_ltcwithin6 cdph_hivdiagwhen cdph_hivdiagdate w1idate w2idate w3idate, by(su_id)
        5.  replace cdph_earliestafterdiag = .c if cdph_hivdiagwhen>"Before W3":cdph_hivdiagwhen
        6.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace cdph_earliestafterdiag = w1_cdph_earliestafterdiag if
            mi(cdph_earliestafterdiag) & !mi(w1_cdph_earliestafterdiag)
        7.  WAVE 3 CHANGE:replace cdph_earliestafterdiag = w2_cdph_earliestafterdiag if
            mi(cdph_earliestafterdiag) & !mi(w2_cdph_earliestafterdiag)

            categorized under clubbar_downtown_vltrd. Respondent is 1 on clubbar_downtown_vltrd if his
            response on the othspec variable could be categorized under clubbar_downtown_vltrd.

      nmalesp:
        1.  replace nmalesp=.c if nspartners==0
        2.  by su_id (alterorder6mo): egen tempv = count(partnersex) if partnersex=="Male":partnersex &
            !mi(alterorder6mo)
        3.  egen nmalesp= mean(tempv)
        4.  replace nmalesp=0 if nmalesp==.
        5.  Num Male Partners

            interview)
